Citations
Date: 0/0/1868
Source: Growing Better Wool
Author: HENDERSON
Vol / Page: 60
Edition:
Quote: Drainage of moisture into the fleece may be helped by a pronounced dip ('devil's grip') behind the shoulder and drainage may be hindered by a broad flat back.
